Testing of Stake holder approval notifications

1. Navigate here to create a new record: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications.do%3Fsys_id%3D-1%26sys_is_list%3Dtrue%26sys_target%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications%26sysparm_checked_items%3D%26sysparm_fixed_query%3D%26sysparm_group_sort%3D%26sysparm_list_css%3D%26sysparm_query%3D%26sysparm_referring_url%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications_list.do%253fsysparm_clear_stack%253dtrue%26sysparm_target%3D%26sysparm_view%3D
2. Fill out the mandatory fields on the record.
3. Add Approval -- Insurance Services for the Approvers
4. Click the UI Action set to Submitted.
5. Click the UI Action Send for Stakeholder Approval
6. As a admin navigate to https://cmudev01.service-now.com/sys_email_list.do?sysparm_query=sys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.beginningOfToday()@javascript:gs.endOfToday()&sysparm_first_row=1&sysparm_view=sent
7. Click the ‘Created’ column to sort by most recently created
8. Find the email with the recipient dianep@andrew.cmu.edu and a subject of (number) Approval Needed for Short Description. Click into this email by clicking the date.
9. Scroll down to the related links and click ‘Preview HTML body’ and review the email body.
10. Navigate back to the installation application previously created.
11. Add a comment in the ‘Additional Comments’ variable and click ‘Post’
12. As a admin navigate to https://cmudev01.service-now.com/sys_email_list.do?sysparm_query=sys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.beginningOfToday()@javascript:gs.endOfToday()&sysparm_first_row=1&sysparm_view=sent
13. Click the ‘Created’ column to sort by most recently created
14. Find the email with the recipient dianep@andrew.cmu.edu and a subject of (number) -  Application for Test has a new comment. Click into this email by clicking the date.
15. Scroll down to the related links and click ‘Preview HTML body’ and review the email body.
16. Navigate back to the installation application previously created.
17. Click the Send for Dean of Students Approval UI Action
18. As a admin navigate to https://cmudev01.service-now.com/sys_email_list.do?sysparm_query=sys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.beginningOfToday()@javascript:gs.endOfToday()&sysparm_first_row=1&sysparm_view=sent
19. Click the ‘Created’ column to sort by most recently created
20. Find the email with the recipient dianep@andrew.cmu.edu and a subject of (number) -  (short description) has been approved
21. Scroll down to the related links and click ‘Preview HTML body’ and review the email body.

