Testing Informed on Approval

32. Navigate back to the installation application previously created.
33. Add Alessandro Molteni to the Informed on Approval variable.
34. Click the Save UI Action
35. Click the Approve the Application UI Action
36. As a admin navigate to https://cmudev01.service-now.com/sys_email_list.do?sysparm_query=sys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.beginningOfToday()@javascript:gs.endOfToday()&sysparm_first_row=1&sysparm_view=sent
37. Click the ‘Created’ column to sort by most recently created
38. Find the email with the recipient am74@andrew.cmu.edu and a subject of (number) -  Projects and Installations Application for (short description) has been approved
39. Scroll down to the related links and click ‘Preview HTML body’ and review the email body.
